One of us! One of us!  Seriously though, none of us care what race you are or what you believe in, we are all here just for tendies. All are welcome and were happy to have you here. These posts are just to garner hate for the sub, but look at my username. Sure I could be a white cis male, or I could be a fucking platypus who is cognizant of financial markets and goes to trade on the Cincinnati zoo computers when the zookeepers arent looking. No one knows. 

&amp;#x200B;

Seriously though, if any of you are in Cincinnati and happen to see the platypus exhibit at the zoo, drop some chicken tenders into those guys. they are super cool.
